el in the bio, where I share more on all things spirituality, mindfulness and nervous system regulation 🤍\n\n#mindfulness #nervoussystemhealing #spirituality #spiritual #mindfulmoments", "duration": 90.349, "timestamp": 1773031068, "uploader_id": "61348510818", "uploader": "Kate ☀️", "channel": "very.kat", "like_count": 289, "comment_count": 12, "comments": [{"author": "zenith303", "author_id": "467850060", "id": "18312687868260490", "text": "🙌", "timestamp": 1774955012}, {"author": "wallie_autry", "author_id": "262110822", "id": "18547811725067694", "text": "🔥", "timestamp": 1774743057}, {"author": "richard.vandenbosch", "author_id": "4801536164", "id": "18098060561003401", "text": "❤️", "timestamp": 1774385014}, {"author": "jamesthomasdonovan", "author_id": "3584761829", "id": "18096768332292942", "text": "You are killing me.🎼🎵🎶power to ya.", "timestamp": 1773885744}, {"author": "mahawoody", "author_id": "77097960712", "id": "18259709230293362", "text": "Another great post. Once diagnosed bipolar , after studying with monks in Japan, gave up smoking, drinking, drugs like cocaine, eating meat and even the prescription drugs for my condition.All on the same day 45 yrs ago. Things can change quickly, and you don't realize you have been traveling the path to that day for a very long time possibly.", "timestamp": 1773646081}, {"author": "franksinatra127", "author_id": "2237078841", "id": "18444273298128005", "text": "😍😍😍😍", "timestamp": 1773432852}, {"author": "progressps4", "author_id": "48919770870", "id": "18304794538278668", "text": "I'd just like a little benchmark every now and again to show me im doing the right thing or help me see through the fog", "timestamp": 1773137296}, {"author": "msgblum", "author_id": "5796298951", "id": "17930724240207275", "text": "I've been following your posts. I appreciate your evocative content and the good intentions behind them.", "timestamp": 1773093304}, {"author": "seldom314", "author_id": "53362516636", "id": "17973523251006900", "text": "Yes", "timestamp": 1773078909}, {"author": "charles_cox23", "author_id": "5364026026", "id": "18076390235113977", "text": "🙏", "timestamp": 1773051944}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649492174_17960910783046819_1875738254427560383_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p640x640_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMTE4eDE5ODAuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFTw1JpLA9JE0YCMm4wNT6hX-_iMoNW1C1tWztWInIAFgnpxlioKyXhdKF--ZUxss8&_nc_ohc=9qffxBwzBvAQ7kNvwE7Lh4C&_nc_gid=qxuhg-hsLr9CDWU4Vem7pA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0ztlcuoWQLYU0gX0tcd-xllRs2VmqPMgjr_mTN-tjxCg&oe=69DE20F1&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1133, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1133"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649492174_17960910783046819_1875738254427560383_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p750x750_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMTE4eDE5ODAuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFTw1JpLA9JE0YCMm4wNT6hX-_iMoNW1C1tWztWInIAFgnpxlioKyXhdKF--ZUxss8&_nc_ohc=9qffxBwzBvAQ7kNvwE7Lh4C&_nc_gid=qxuhg-hsLr9CDWU4Vem7pA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af1HKHLC7ZjLCbmAvARtvEhhfOMuIDys1kUdDZeVUX62Cg&oe=69DE20F1&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 750, "height": 1328, "id": "1", "resolution": "750x1328"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/649492174_17960910783046819_1875738254427560383_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh0.08_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi4xMTE4eDE5ODAuc2RyLmY4Mjc4Ny5kZWZhdWx0X2NvdmVyX2ZyYW1lLmMyIn0&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=107&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFTw1JpLA9JE0YCMm4wNT6hX-_iMoNW1C1tWztWInIAFgnpxlioKyXhdKF--ZUxss8&_nc_ohc=9qffxBwzBvAQ7kNvwE7Lh4C&_nc_gid=qxuhg-hsLr9CDWU4Vem7pA&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af08Y2O1j9Y2-jsAMI-L9CTY0l5Jc6XxVQJGlzzHchkdog&oe=69DE20F1&_nc_sid=d885a2"